data.description: Introducing an exquisite home for sale that embodies pristine finishes, versatility, and ample storage space. This gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with rocking chair front porch is located in Lakes and Streams. The property boasts a range of desirable features, including  a flexible living space with all bedrooms upstairs and a custom spacious master closet. The fourth bedroom is generously-sized with a sitting area to the side. Downstairs you will find an open concept living area, office space, and an outdoor storage room. Neighborhood amenities include 8 lakes, walking trails, green space and numerous fountains. Call today for your showing. OFFERING 4.99 % INTEREST RATE WITH PREFERRED LENDER, $4,000 SELLER PAID CLOSING COSTS and 6 months-lawn care until 12/31/23.
